    <item>
      <title>英伟达股价一波三折，涨幅达 591,078%，成为市值最高的股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/nvidia-s-591-078-rally-to-most-valuable-stock-came-in-waves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[1999 年，乔布斯刚刚回归苹果公司，英特尔是半导体行业的主导力量，而一家名不见经传的芯片制造商 Nvidia 在纳斯达克证券交易所首次亮相。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/nvidia-s-591-078-rally-to-most-valuable-stock-came-in-waves</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 20:30:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
